      <ab type="lido:objectDescriptionSet">Aleksandar ‘Saša’ Petrović at a reception in the company of two women. Petrović and the women are smiling and holding glasses in their hands.</ab>
      <ab subtype="comment" type="lido:objectDescriptionSet">Petrović was one of Europe’s leading directors of the 1960s and one of the major figures of a wave of critical Yugoslav films in the 1960s and early 1970s. In 1973, he was dismissed from the Belgrade film academy after being accused of holding anti-communist views.</ab>
